### Component 4: Backend Routes & Main Router

#### [NEW] [rag.py](file:///d:/Nisarg.Doc/Skaps/chatbot/backend/app/routes/rag.py)
- Exposes standard API endpoints as requested in `rag-prompt.md`:
  - `POST /api/rag/upload`: Direct file ingest.
  - `POST /api/rag/chat`: Performs RAG completion (grounded question answering).
  - `DELETE /api/rag/documents/{document_id}`: Standard deletion hook.
- Mounts routes in `backend/app/main.py` under prefix `/api/rag`.

#### [MODIFY] [admin.py](file:///d:/Nisarg.Doc/Skaps/chatbot/backend/app/routes/admin.py)
- Automatically triggers `ingest_document` in a background thread upon file upload in `POST /api/admin/documents/upload` to seamlessly index documents inside Qdrant.
- Automatically calls `delete_document_chunks` upon document deletion in `DELETE /api/admin/documents/{doc_id}` to keep Qdrant synced with PostgreSQL!

